flowchart TD

A([Start])

B[/Enter PIN/]

C{PIN correct?}

D[Incorrect PIN]

E{3 attempts used?}

F[Card blocked]

G[/Enter withdrawal amount/]

H{Multiple of 20 TL?}

I{Enough balance?}

J{Daily limit exceeded?}

K[Dispense cash and update balance]

L{Another transaction?}

M([End])

A --> B
B --> C

C -- Yes --> G
C -- No --> D

D --> E
E -- Yes --> F
E -- No --> B

G --> H

H -- No --> G
H -- Yes --> I

I -- No --> G
I -- Yes --> J

J -- Yes --> G
J -- No --> K

K --> L

L -- Yes --> G
L -- No --> M

F --> M
